  "image": "/images/coming-soon.jpg",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Lesson 32",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 0.23,
      "endTime": 2.17,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Lesson",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "课程，第...课"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "A lost ship",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.18,
      "endTime": 9.02
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Did the crew of the Elkor find what they were looking for? Why?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 9.03,
      "endTime": 15.37,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The salvage operation had been a complete failure.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 15.38,
      "endTime": 19.19
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The small ship, Elkor, which had been searching the Barents Sea for weeks, was on its way home.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 19.2,
      "endTime": 26.71,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "A radio message from the mainland had been received by the ship's captain instructing him to give up the search.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 26.72,
      "endTime": 34.52
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The captain knew that another attempt would be made later,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 34.53,
      "endTime": 38.09,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "for the sunken ship he was trying to find had been carrying a precious cargo of gold bullion.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 38.1,
      "endTime": 45.32
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Despite the message, the captain of the Elkor decided to try once more.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 45.33,
      "endTime": 51.88
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The sea bed was scoured with powerful nets and there was tremendous excitement on board when a chest was raised from the bottom.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 51.89,
      "endTime": 60.75
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Though the crew were at first under the impression that the lost ship had been found,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 60.76,
      "endTime": 65.98,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "the contents of the chest proved them wrong.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 65.99,
      "endTime": 69.51
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What they had in fact found was a ship which had been sunk many years before.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 69.52,
      "endTime": 75.61,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The chest contained the personal belongings of a seaman, Alan Fielding.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 75.62,
      "endTime": 80.75
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "There were books, clothing and photographs, together with letters which the seaman had once received from his wife.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 80.76,
      "endTime": 88.33,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The captain of the Elkor ordered his men to salvage as much as possible from the wreck.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 88.34,
      "endTime": 94.31,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Much",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Nothing of value was found,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 94.32,
      "endTime": 96.47
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but the numerous items which were brought to the surface proved to be of great interest.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 96.48,
      "endTime": 101.74
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "From a heavy gun that was raised, the captain realized that the ship must have been a cruiser.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 101.75,
      "endTime": 108,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "In another chest which contained the belongings of a ship's officer,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 108.01,
      "endTime": 112.67
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "there was an unfinished letter which had been written on March 14th, 1943.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 112.68,
      "endTime": 120
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The captain learnt from the letter that the name of the lost ship was the Karen.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 120.01,
      "endTime": 125.2,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Name",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "名字"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The most valuable find of all was the ship's log book, parts of which it was still possible to read.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 125.21,
      "endTime": 133.4,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Book",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "书"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "From this the captain was able to piece together all the information that had come to light.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 133.41,
      "endTime": 139.05,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The Karen had been sailing in a convoy to Russia when she was torpedoed by an enemy submarine.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 139.06,
      "endTime": 145.62
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "This was later confirmed by a naval official at the Ministry of Defence after the Elkor had returned home.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 145.63,
      "endTime": 153.15,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "All the items that were found were sent to the War Museum.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 153.16,
      "endTime": 158.16,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
